<div id="readme">
<h2>New Life Of Luck</h2>
<ul>

<li><strong>High Concept:</strong>
Try to aquire enough money to start a new life through playing lottery scratch cards.
</li>

<li><strong>Player Experience Goals:</strong>
I want the player to experience that their choices have a great impact on the game. If they play risky
they could come out on top or fall all the way to the bottom.
</li>

<li><strong>Genre:</strong>
Luck
</li>

<li><strong>Game play:</strong>
Click on a card to buy it, click on the hidden numbers to reveal them. Some of the cards have
 different ways to win so read the card instructions.
</li>

<li><strong>Prototype goal:</strong>
My goal was to make a game with different way to play and win.
</li>

<li><strong>Features:</strong>
This game features five different lottery sratch cards. 
</li>

<li><strong>Setting/Premise:</strong>
The setting is at a convience store.
</li>

<li><strong>Story:</strong>
Your life is going down hill and all you want to do is escape and start new. Right now you can't 
 due to lacking of funds. Play the lottery to get enough money to leave it all and start fresh.
</li>

<li><strong>Target Audience:</strong>
Anyone
</li>

<li><strong>Play time:</strong>
2 - 7 minuites
</li>

<li><strong>Strategies:</strong>
Learn to play the random generater. The correct combination of different cards could heelp you win faster.
</li>

<li><strong>Prototype Assets:</strong>
I created all of my own assets!
</li>

<li><strong>Prototype Closest Other Game:</strong>

</li>

</ul>
